race.comment: BEAUTY EDGE (4) appreciated the drop in class and distance when a comfortable winner over this trip at Dubbo 17 days ago. Speedy customer who might have found his niche at 1000m. Can win again. DESIROUS (8) made a sustained run from before the corner then cleared out for an impressive win in a similar race to this at Warren last time out. No reason she cannot deliver a similar performance here. CROOK (6) caught the eye in the closing stages when resuming over this distance at Warren recently. Lightly raced mare who will benefit from that hit-out and can feature in the finish. CAN DO IT (5) has outstanding stats here at this trip. Stormed home to finish second at Dubbo last time. Watch for a big final furlong. Veteran OBSESSIVE NATURE (1) has seven wins to his name at this trip. Carries weight well and is not out of contention on a six-week freshen up.
